The average in Eq. (8) for a temperature T can be obtained by considering a single distorted atomic configuration, which is created by displacing the atoms by an amount of Δτkα from the equilibrium structure35:11Δτkα=MpMk∑ν3N−3−1(ν−1)ekα,νσν,T,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
